{
  "stem": "13471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a big hiatus there, the Navy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why the Navy?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to go into a little family history.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The name Steer-- There's, there's a family tradition.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The name Steer is supposedly due to the fact that the man who steered or piloted William the Conqueror across the Channel before he beat the British in the Battle of Hastings in 1066 AD was the original Steer.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I don't know-- know anything about Viking ships, but the-- the Viking steering oar-- they didn't have a rudder-- steering oar was over the starboard side.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the way, I called starboard-- it's steerboard, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Starboard.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would steer the ship from the steering oar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at the same time, with his left-- that was his right hand-- with his left hand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He would handle a sheet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the sheet, to you landlubbers, is the rope that controls the sails, you see?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he was the, the pilot and the steersman and everything else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you look at the tapestry, what's that tapestry?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- the famous tapestry that describes the invasion of England by-- anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Named for a French town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can't think of it, that's terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You can see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's a picture of him, sitting there in the stern [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father told me this when-- when I was a boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said-- on my 12th birthday, he said, now, this is a family tradition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was told this by my father on my 12th birthday, I'm telling you, I want you to tell your son on your 12th birthday.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First of all, they were Quakers.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
